        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer22115958" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16734286632234316041">hehe. I&apos;m such a naughty girl for picking this one up. I had watched the movie &quot;Quills&quot; and became terribly curious about Marquis de Sade. After the first 20 pages, I must say that my cup of interest was filled in it&apos;s entirety, but I kept reading because the perversion of his writing was so unbelievable and even humorous. (I must state, that this novel is considered his most joyous writing... MOST of the sexual escapades in in violent deaths.) I couldn&apos;t believe that a man could have such a cre</span>
  <span id="freeText16734286632234316041" style="display:none">hehe. I'm such a naughty girl for picking this one up. I had watched the movie "Quills" and became terribly curious about Marquis de Sade. After the first 20 pages, I must say that my cup of interest was filled in it's entirety, but I kept reading because the perversion of his writing was so unbelievable and even humorous. (I must state, that this novel is considered his most joyous writing... MOST of the sexual escapades in in violent deaths.) I couldn't believe that a man could have such a creatively dirty mind. My face was red when I bought it, but it was scarlett when I read it! </span>
  <a data-text-id="16734286632234316041" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

