  <span id="freeText4700671296572438521" style="display:none">I came across Marquis De Sade in a Pete Doherty interview as he was mentioned to be the first and ultimate libertine which got me interested and after a quick Google search I found he is quite the character. Born in the seventeen century, Marquis was quite unusual and the word sadism was directly taken from his name and invented for him and his behaviour. <br /><br />I can't describe this book, you will have to read this for yourself. I myself am fascinated by de Sade and his behaviour and therefore will read all his works but be warned going in, most dark romance written today pales beside the writings of this guy.</span>
