  <span id="freeText16333907914793687228" style="display:none"><b>Edited March 27, 2015.</b><br /><br />Dear bookclub,<br /><br />I am so sorry!!<br /><br />Where to begin? This book is a monster. Not because of its length, but because of the depths of its depravity.<br /><br />There is graphic buggery on every page. There are plenty of anti-mom sentiments. And also anti-family propaganda. We are told that the greatest pleasure in life is buggery-- and not hetero-buggery between man and woman-- but homo-buggery of man with boy. This is supposedly because of natural inclination and because (a) males have a more pleasing ass shape with rounder butts, whereas women's butts tend to be wider, and (b) males have softer pinker assholes (???).<br /><br /><b>PLEASE note: I am not against homosexual behavior in any way. I do, however, would prefer it if homosexual assfucking and heterosexual assfucking were portrayed as equal, instead of homosexual assfucking depicted as the peak of all pleasure.</b><br /><br />What else can you expect to find within these pages?<br /><br />Rationalization of:<br />+ theft<br />+ rape<br />+ vindictive punishment<br />+ murder<br /><br />Encouragement of:<br />+ incest<br />+ double penetration<br />+ sodomy <br />+ abortion (I am pro-abortion, but to just blatantly encourage abortion because pregnancy ruins the woman's figure is too much for me.)<br />+ libertinage (aka promiscuity)<br />+ polyamory<br />+ adultery<br />+ homosexuality <br />+ bisexuality <br />+ selfishness in all relationships <br /><br />Rants against:<br />+ God and religion <br />+ government <br />+ the wealthy<br />+ filial piety<br />+ mother / daughter relationships<br />+ father / son relationships<br />+ and more generally, the "fake love" between parent + child, and child + parent<br /><br /><br />Includes:<br />+ popping of cherry with massive dick<br />+ daughter sodomizing her mom, having a syphilis-ridden dude infect her mom, and then the daughter sews up her mom's twat and bunghole so that the syphilis juice doesn't drip out<br /><br />* * *<br /><br />I did really like a small portion toward the end which lightly touched upon political philosophy. <br /><br />* * *<br /><br />I do admire this book because of its outrageousness and outlandishness. But I often thought de Sade seemed to be outrageous just for the sake of being outrageous. Was his intent to push every button? If so, he succeeded. <br /><br />It's an over-powering book which should be read only in small chunks.<br /><br />I'm surprised this was written when it was. It seemed light-years ahead of its time.<br /><br />* * *<br /><br /><br />+ "By what right will he who has nothing be enchained by an agreement which protects only him who has everything?"<br /><br />+ "The situation created by the pledge to respect property the nation has just required all the citizens to subscribe to under oath; by it only the rich enchain the poor, the rich alone benefit from a bargain into which the poor man enters so thoughtlessly, failing to see that through this oath wrung from his good faith, he engages himself to do a thing that cannot be done with respect to himself."<br /><br />+ "Is theft, whose effect is to distribute wealth more evenly, to be branded as a wrong in our day, under our government which aims at equality?"<br /><br />+ "What is man? And what difference is there between him and other plants, between him and all the other animals of the world? None, obviously."<br /><br />+ "How I love to handle your prick while I discharge. I'd have it drown me in fuck, so frig it. Suck me. Oh, heavenly fuck. How I love to play the whore."<br /><br />+ "One fucks because we are born to fuck, because by fucking we obey and fulfill nature's ordinations, and because all man-made laws which would contravene Nature's are made for naught but our contempt."<br /><br />+ "A girl risks having a child only in proportion to the frequency with which she permits the man to invade her cunt. Let her scrupulously avoid this manner of tasting delight; in its stead let her offer indiscriminately her hand, her mouth, her breasts or her ass. This last thoroughfare will yield her considerable pleasure, far more, indeed than any other; by means of the others she will give pleasure."</span>
